OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784391489
OL,3,CPSNI confirm death of 26-year-old
OL,4,Cmotorcyclist in Co Antrim crash
OL,6,FA 26-year-old man has died in a crash
OL,7,Fin Co Antrim.
OL,9,FThe PSNI said it was alerted to a
OL,10,Fcrash between a blue Yamaha motorcycle
OL,11,Fand a blue Skoda Enyaq in the
OL,12,FBallymena Road area of Doagh at the
OL,13,Fjunction of Deer Park Road at around
OL,14,F1.40pm on Friday.
OL,16,FThe Northern Ireland Ambulance Service
OL,17,Falso attended but the motorcyclist, 26-
OL,18,Fyear-old Jamie Fleming, was pronounced
OL,19,Fdead at the scene.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
