OL,3,CPSNI confirm death of 26-year-old
OL,4,Cmotorcyclist in Co Antrim crash
OL,6,FMr Fleming was from the Ballyclare
OL,7,Farea.
OL,9,FDetective Inspector Stewart, from the
OL,10,FCollision Investigation Unit, said:
OL,11,F"Our inquiries are continuing and we
OL,12,Fwould appeal to anyone who witnessed
OL,13,Fthe collision, or who may have any
OL,14,Finformation which could assist with
OL,15,Four investigation, including dashcam
OL,16,For other footage, to contact the
OL,17,FCollision Investigation Unit on 101,
OL,18,Fquoting reference number 827 of 17/07/
OL,19,F26."
